request.description:
Login to get access token

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "email": "owner@thedunes.com",
  "password": "owner123"
}
```

**Success Response (200):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": {
    "en": "Login successful"
  },
  "data": {
    "accessToken": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
    "tokenType": "Bearer",
    "employee": {
      "id": 1,
      "name": "Owner",
      "email": "owner@thedunes.com",
      "position": "Owner",
      "statusEmployee": "ACTIVE",
      "permissions": {
        "overviewScreen": true,
        "settingScreen": true
      }
    }
  }
}
```

**Error Response (401):**
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "error": "Invalid email or password",
  "message": {
    "en": "Invalid email or password"
  }
}
```

**Note:** Token is automatically saved to environment variable `accessToken`

